           </script><![endif]--></head><body id="body"><header id="nav_archive" class="blue_bar"><a href="/" class="title"><span id="back_to_blog"></span><img class="avatar" src="http://37.media.tumblr.com/avatar_a1cc9a72d388_40.png" alt="" /><h1 class="blog_title">The Old Reader: behind the scenes</h1></a><div id="browse_months"><div id="jump_to_month"><span class="month">Month </span><span class="arrow"></span></div></div><nav id="register" class="nav_right"><iframe scrolling="no" frameborder="0" id="tumblr_controls" src="http://assets.tumblr.com/assets/html/archive_iframe.html?_v=52da664eee1ddc7983f50df1b3e39816#src=http%3A%2F%2Fblog.theoldreader.com%2Farchive%2F2013%2F11%3Fbefore_time%3D1384356811&amp;name=theoldreader" width="400" height="28" style="border:0; background-color:transparent; overflow:hidden; "></iframe></nav></header><div class="l-content"><!-- START CONTENT --><header class="heading" style="display:none;"><h2 class="date">October 2013</h2><h3 class="post_count">1 post</h3></header><section id="posts_201310" class="posts loading" style="display:none;"><div class="post post_micro is_regular post_tumblelog_251da5c449b4f29e623ce0c1997fea71 not_mine is_original with_permalink no_source has_hover" id="post_micro_62807343695"  data-post-id='62807343695' data-root-id='62807343695' data-tumblelog-name='theoldreader' data-tumblelog-key='Ux21axKm0' data-reblog-key='wNquRdlB' data-type='regular' data-serve-id='0.23788000 1406167763892027312' data-json='{"post-id":"62807343695","root-id":"62807343695","tumblelog-name":"theoldreader","tumblelog-key":"Ux21axKm0","reblog-key":"wNquRdlB","type":"regular","serve-id":"0.23788000 1406167763892027312","json":"{\u0022post-id\u0022:\u002262807343695\u0022,\u0022root-id\u0022:\u002262807343695\u0022,\u0022tumblelog-name\u0022:\u0022theoldreader\u0022,\u0022tumblelog-key\u0022:\u0022Ux21axKm0\u0022,\u0022reblog-key\u0022:\u0022wNquRdlB\u0022,\u0022type\u0022:\u0022regular\u0022,\u0022serve-id\u0022:\u00220.23788000 1406167763892027312\u0022}"}'><div class="post_content"><div class="post_content_inner"><div class="post_title">Apps!</div><p><p><img class="toggle_inline_image inline_image constrained_image" src="http://media.tumblr.com/b08bde2eb091d291e81fcae8b3384ef9/tumblr_inline_mtzs96IZD91r33zvf.png" alt="image" /></p></p>

<p>We&#8217;d like to take a minute to thank the community of applications developers that have assisted in improving the user experience and accessibility of The Old Reader.  Please take a moment to <a href="http://theoldreader.com/pages/apps">browse the list </a>and let us know if there is anything we&#8217;re missing.  New apps are still being added and developed specifically for The Old Reader and we&#8217;re thrilled to say that other prominent applications have us on the shortlist to be supported soon.</p>
<p>Along these same lines, please know that all of your feedback and voting at <a href="http://theoldreader.uservoice.com/">UserVoice</a> is appreciated and something we take very seriously.  Our first priority has been to transition The Old Reader and improve the architecture and performance.  As many of you have noted, we&#8217;ve made huge strides in that area.  In the near future, we plan to communicate more around specific features and begin making functional improvements.</p>
<p>Thanks for using The Old Reader!</p></div></div><div class="post_glass post_micro_glass" 
     title=""><a target="_blank" class="hover"
               title=""
